Biblio-Thesaurus-SQLite version 0.01
====================================

This module tries to manage a ISO Thesaurus into a SQLite database.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

	sqlite
	Biblio::Thesaurus
	DBIx::Simple
	DBD::SQLite

